    "When you're ready, keep writing—a line in Gratitudes, Needs, and People in Mind is enough to begin. Tap the status above anytime if you want a gentle reminder." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When you're ready, keep writing—a line in Gratitudes, Needs, and People in Mind is enough to begin. Tap the status above anytime if you want a gentle reminder."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "不用着急，想写的时候继续就好。先写 1 件感恩的事、1 件需要的事和 1 位牵挂的人，就已经开始了。想再看看说明，随时点按上方状态。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can keep writing in Gratitudes, Needs, and People in Mind if you'd like a fuller reflection. Tap the status above anytime to read about Harvest." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You can keep writing in Gratitudes, Needs, and People in Mind if you'd like a fuller reflection. Tap the status above anytime to read about Harvest."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你想写得更完整一些，也可以继续写下去，把感恩的事、需要的事和牵挂的人再多记几条。想进一步了解「丰收」时，随时点按上方状态即可。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
